title: Bug 7945: Search results not selected in external jar
description: Bug 7945: Search results not selected in external jar Build 200201151. Search for references to this field. When double-clicking on the search result, the first match is not selected.
OB: When double-clicking on the search result, the first match is not selected.
EB: When double-clicking on the search result, you should get 3 matches in method getTempDir() within the search results.
SR:
1. Open the search feature.
2. Search for references to this field.
3. Observe the search results.
4. Double-click on the search result.
5. Observe that the first match is not selected.
